statements: SELECT * FROM market_data;
SELECT symbol, price FROM market_data WHERE volume > 1000 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT symbol, volume FROM market_data WHERE price > 50 ORDER BY symbol ASC, timestamp DESC;
SELECT timestamp, price, volume, symbol FROM market_data LIMIT 10 OFFSET 5;
SELECT symbol, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM market_data GROUP BY symbol;
SELECT symbol, price, volume, timestamp FROM market_data WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price DESC
SELECT * FROM market_data WHERE volume >= 5000 ORDER BY timestamp ASC
SELECT symbol, price FROM market_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31' AND volume < 10000 ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT symbol, AVG(price) as avg_price FROM market_data GROUP BY symbol HAVING avg_price > 50 ORDER BY avg_price DESC
SELECT symbol, COUNT(*) as total_records FROM market_data WHERE price < 50 GROUP BY symbol HAVING total_records > 5 ORDER BY total_records DESC
SELECT symbol, price, volume, timestamp FROM MarketData WHERE symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT * FROM MarketData WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT symbol, price FROM MarketData WHERE volume > 10000 AND timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT MAX(price) AS max_price, MIN(price) AS min_price FROM MarketData;
SELECT symbol, COUNT(*) AS trades_count FROM TradingDecisions GROUP BY symbol ORDER BY trades_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM MarketData WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT symbol, volume FROM MarketData WHERE volume BETWEEN 1000 AND 5000 ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT MAX(price) AS highest_price FROM MarketData WHERE symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT symbol, COUNT(*) AS count_decisions FROM TradingDecisions GROUP BY symbol HAVING count_decisions > 5;
SELECT * FROM MarketData m LEFT JOIN TradingDecisions td ON m.symbol = td.symbol WHERE td.decision = 'BUY' AND m.timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY m.price DESC, td.timestamp ASC;
